        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You've mastered combat practices that let you get up close and bring down perpetrators alive.</p>\n<p>You can use your Intelligence modifier on attack rolls when you @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Devise a Stratagem]{Devise a Strategem} if you're using a weapon of the club group in one hand (like a club, staff, or sap), in addition to the usual weapons, and those Strikes qualify for your @Compendium[pf2e.classfeatures.Strategic Strike]{Strategic Strike}.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you can make any of your Strikes nonlethal without taking the normal -2 penalty.</p>"
